OL,5, Customers at one of the UK's biggest   
OL,6, housebuilders are taking out longer    
OL,7, mortgages to make monthly repayments   
OL,8, more affordable.                       
OL,10,FTaylor Wimpey said 27% of first time   
OL,11,Fbuyers are taking mortgages of more    
OL,12,Fthan 36 years compared to 7% in 2021.  
OL,14,FWhile extending mortgage terms means   
OL,15,Flower monthly payments, customers can  
OL,16,Fend up paying more overall.            
OL,18,FMortgage rates have been soaring as the
OL,19,FBank of England raises interest rates  
OL,20,Fto try to get inflation under control. 
